---
title: Warm Pear, Feta & Chicken Salad with Walnut Panko, Pickled Shallot & Blue Cheese Dressing
description: This festive main course salad is destined to become a hit on your table! You’ll toss a bright mix of fresh greens, tender sautéed pear, and quick-pickled shallot with creamy blue cheese dressing and briny crumbled feta. Shower your salad with crunchy walnut-panko topping for a harmonious blend of flavors and textures.
